resources.string: TopSecret
Once upon a time there was a man named Andrew who was browsing Tinder…
when he saw the most beautiful girl, whose name was Jenna, and immediately swiped right.
Jenna thought Andrew\'s opening was going to be a dick joke, but instead it was the start of a beautiful relationship…
On December 21st 2014 they decided to meet in person and take a walk around Moore Mesa, where they bonded over their crazy families and watched the sunset.
They went their separate ways over Christmas break but they were constantly texting and sharing photos.
On January 3rd 2015, they took a moonlit walk along the beach, where they kissed for the first time. Although the beach was cold they stayed out until 4 am.
For their first public date they went to see Gone Girl. Surprisingly, Andrew did not runaway (jk)
Soon after they became smitten with each other and would spend most of their spare time together. In their spare time they partook in activities such as…
Bowling, eating, watching soccer, going to the beach and…
Watching The Grand Budapest Hotel. ;)
Things were going swimmingly until, Andrew…
broke his ankle and would need surgery.
Instead of saying peace out, Jenna, being an amazing girlfriend stuck by Andrew’s side. She would come over immediately after work and school to help nurse him back to health.
She slept over every night, and the best part was in the middle of the night Andrew would wake her up for a quick kiss before letting her drift back to sleep.

Life was easier once Andrew transitioned to a scooter and crutches. They even were able to see book of Mormon, and meet Jenna\'s family, which was a struggle because of Zeus\' tail and their tri-level house
Jenna graduated college, and she moved in with Andrew, as they practically already lived together, and she screwed out of a job
At Jenna\'s Graduation party in Sac, Andrew escaped the crowd to go to the bedroom where he wrote a simple program, to tell Jenna that he loves her for the first time.
Life strolled blissfully along, as the happy couple enjoyed their life together.
Spring Break 2016, they traveled to D.C. and Albany to see family…
and to NYC where they met up with Alex
In July of 2017, Andrew and Jenna took a plunge and moved to Portland so Andrew could jump start his career.
Not too long after moving, Jenna was able to find a job which she enjoys… for the most part.
They soon came to love Portland with its laid back vibe, food, beautiful nature and Jenna\'s favorite…
They immersed themselves in the culture and became staunch Blazers fans, who have now attended over 15 games and know whole roster
Over this past winter break, they went off to the east coast again. It was the coldest either had experienced before. Plus weren’t told to pack proper shoes.
Still they had a blast seeing family and friends in New York and Boston. In Boston they met up with Yvette and Tanya where they attended a classy New Years Eve Party
For Jenna\'s 25th birthday they traveled to Canada with her siblings. This was their first time together in a new country.
They are currently spending a week in the exotic land of Hawaii, enjoying their amazing life, but…
There is one things missing, and one question to ask…
Jenna,
